      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for someone looking for a functional car at a lower price point. The exterior shows its age with some minor paint fading and a few small dings, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may require some upcoming maintenance on the suspension and brakes to ensure long-term reliability. It is a solid, honest car that reflects its years of use but still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
