    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a responsive engine and a transmission that shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver. The exterior is clean and retains a nice luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with no tears in the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as intended. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that offers a great balance of performance and aesthetic appeal without needing any immediate repairs.",
