      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance and lasting aesthetic appeal. This specimen represents a superb balance of value and reliability, having undergone a rigorous inspection to verify its mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. Ideal for the discerning driver who demands quality and dependability, it arrives prepared for immediate service. Experience the assurance of a vehicle that has been treated with the utmost care by its previous stewards.",
