    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. Suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded bushings. While the chassis and interior show honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the drivetrain integrity is paramount. A pure enthusiast spec ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 31500.0,
